 />\nCristina Pellegrini</strong></p>\n<h3>Padua</h3>\n<p>Veneto Institute of Oncology IOV - IRCCS<br />\nImmunology and Diagnostics Molecular Oncology Unit</p>\n<p>Member: <strong>Chiara Menin</strong></p>\n<p>Cancer Genomics Program</p>\n<p>Member: <strong>Arcangela De Nicolo</strong></p>\n<h3>Rome</h3>\n<p>Institute of Dermatology<br />\nCatholic University - Fondazione Policlinico A. Gemelli</p>\n<p>Members: <strong>Ketty Peris (PI)<br />\nLaura Del Regno<br />\nAlessandro Di Stefani</strong></p>\n<h3>Genoa</h3>\n<p>Genetics of Rare Cancers <br /><br />\nDepartment of Internal Medicine and Medical Specialties<br /><br />\nUniversity of Genoa and <br /><br />\nUniversity Hospital Policlinico San Martino</p>\n<p>Members: <strong>Paola Ghiorzo (PI)<br />\nLorenza Pastorino<br />\nWilliam Bruno<br />\nGiulia Ciccarese<br />\nBruna Dalmasso<br />\nMedical Oncology Unit<br />\nPaola Queirolo</strong></p>\n<h3>Bergamo</h3>\n<p>Azienda Ospedaliera Papa Giovanni XXIII </p>\n<p>Members: <strong>Mario Mandala (PI)<br /><br />\nLaura Cattaneo</strong></p>\n<h3>Milan</h3>\n<p>Department of Experimental Oncology and Molecular Medicine<br />\nFondazione IRCCS Istituto Nazionale dei Tumori</p>\n<p>Members: <strong>Monica Rodolfo (PI)</strong></p>\n<h3>Florence</h3>\n<p>Histopathology and Molecular Diagnostics<br />\nCareggi University Hospital</p>\n<p>Members: <strong>Daniela Massi</strong></p>\n<h2>Greece</h2>\n<p> </p>\n<h3>Athens</h3>\n<p>National and Kapodistrian University of Athens School of Medicine<br />\nAndreas Sygros Hospital</p>\n<p>Members: <strong>Alex Stratigos (PI)<br />\nIrene Stefanaki<br />\nVangelis Evangelou<br />\nKaterina Kypreou</strong></p>\n<h3>Ioannina</h3>\n<p>Department of Hygiene and Epidemiology<br />\nUniversity of Ioannina Medical School</p>\n<h3>CYPRUS</h3>\n<p>\n</p><h3>Nicosia</h3>\n<p>Department of Electron Microscopy/Molecular Pathology<br />\nThe Cyprus Institute of Neurology and Genetics<br />\nThe Cyprus School of Molecular Medicine</p>\